# {{.ProjectName}}

A production-ready Go REST API built with {{if eq .ServerType "gin"}}Gin{{else}}Fiber{{end}}, featuring security and observability best practices.

## 🚀 Quick Start

```bash
# Start all services (API, PostgreSQL, Redis)
make up

# Check if the API is running
curl http://localhost:8080/health/ready

# View logs
make logs

# Stop all services
make down
```

